format: html

::: {.cell hash='dados2_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-1_d9475c0889192d34156c45e82d004d92'}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(tidyverse)
library(readxl)

dados2 <- read_excel("dados-dyenici.xlsx", "Dados")

dados2 |> 
  ggplot(aes(fator))+
  geom_histogram(bins = 10  , 
                 fill= 'lightgreen',
                 color= "black")+
  theme_classic()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](dados2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-1-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## Checando as premissas


::: {.cell hash='dados2_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_dc1cdfd7a54c4a38c9e65da08900a540'}

```{.r .cell-code}
dados3 <- aov(fator~material+repetição,
              data= dados2)

summary(dados3)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
            Df Sum Sq Mean Sq F value  Pr(>F)    
material    25 12.371  0.4948   3.361 2.4e-05 ***
repetição    1  0.017  0.0170   0.115   0.735    
Residuals   77 11.337  0.1472                    
---
Signif. codes:  0 '***' 0.001 '**' 0.01 '*' 0.05 '.' 0.1 ' ' 1
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
library(performance)
check_heteroscedasticity(dados3)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
Warning: Heteroscedasticity (non-constant error variance) detected (p < .001).
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
check_normality(dados3)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
Warning: Non-normality of residuals detected (p < .001).
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
library(DHARMa)
plot(simulateResiduals(dados3))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](dados2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-2-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## Transformação Box Cox


::: {.cell hash='dados2_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_d40a77dca39e0f3908bf0d47e8910221'}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(MASS)
b <- boxcox (lm(dados2$fator+0.1 ~ 1))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](dados2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-3-1.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
lambda <- b$x[which.max(b$y)]
lambda
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] -0.7070707
```
:::
:::

::: {.cell hash='dados2_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-4_7244d7c4a22193d993817e57cc9a9ed4'}

```{.r .cell-code}
dados4 <- dados2 |> 
  mutate(fatort=log(fator))

dados4 |> 
  ggplot(aes(fatort))+
  geom_histogram(bbins = 10  , 
                 fill= 'orange',
                 color= "black")+
  theme_classic()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](dados2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## Checando novamente as premissas


::: {.cell hash='dados2_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-5_d5f400c9b1d4bdbe6eb5150d54d28dd2'}

```{.r .cell-code}
dados5 <- aov(fatort ~material+repetição,
              data = dados4)

summary(dados5)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
            Df Sum Sq Mean Sq F value   Pr(>F)    
material    25  76.96   3.078   4.145 8.04e-07 ***
repetição    1   3.61   3.613   4.864   0.0304 *  
Residuals   77  57.18   0.743                     
---
Signif. codes:  0 '***' 0.001 '**' 0.01 '*' 0.05 '.' 0.1 ' ' 1
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
library(performance)
check_heteroscedasticity(dados5)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
OK: Error variance appears to be homoscedastic (p = 0.140).
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
check_normality(dados5)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
Warning: Non-normality of residuals detected (p = 0.002).
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
library(DHARMa)
plot(simulateResiduals(dados5))
```

## Critérios de Moura e Regis (1987)


::: {.cell hash='dados2_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-7_f338783109b3d8fb8bf39722aabcc1d3'}

```{.r .cell-code}
dados6 <- read_excel("dados2.xlsx", "rfr")

dados6 |> 
  ggplot(aes(x=materiais,
             y=rfr*100)) +
  geom_col(fill= "orange",
           color="black" )+
  ylim(0,100)+
  labs(title= "Critérios de Moura e Regis (1987)", 
       x= "Genótipos", y= "Redução no Fator de Reprodução (%)")
```
